時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8udugLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8udugLx.jpg&h=bae3ed34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=710296fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"3b9cbba56b486761995a431f1132e336fcbc25cb","tid":1543652,"uid":173831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cad2803ed1ae997c7494965809621af04595f34","tid":1543652,"uid":206500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6a0266836c08e95671aa12ebfd9509dd4f7d971","tid":1543652,"uid":222212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ed78af606e5de7fddace70ba334a4aa81c63a02","tid":1543652,"uid":228984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7acf05cb6315860b6f80570b0d87bee90a6317c2","tid":1543652,"uid":226392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b7